 </disp-formula>which satisfies the relation 
 <inline-formula>
  <inline-graphic xlink:href="a-75-00842-efi18.jpg" mimetype="image" mime-subtype="gif" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"/>
